# Bolna Local Setup — Deep Analysis

## What Is Bolna?

**Bolna** is an open-source, end-to-end orchestration platform for building **LLM-powered voice agents**. It connects:

- **ASR** (Automatic Speech Recognition) — e.g. Deepgram
- **LLM** (Large Language Model) — e.g. OpenAI, DeepSeek, Llama via LiteLLM
- **TTS** (Text-to-Speech) — e.g. ElevenLabs, AWS Polly, Cartesia, OpenAI
- **Telephony** — Twilio, Plivo (for actual phone calls)

…into a real-time, streaming voice conversation pipeline over **WebSockets**.

---

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Docker Compose Stack
        REDIS["Redis<br/>:6379<br/>Agent & prompt storage"]
        BOLNA["bolna-app<br/>:5001<br/>FastAPI + WebSocket server"]
        NGROK["ngrok<br/>:4040<br/>Public URL tunneling"]
        TWILIO_APP["twilio-app<br/>:8001<br/>Twilio telephony bridge"]
        PLIVO_APP["plivo-app<br/>:8002<br/>Plivo telephony bridge"]
    end

    subgraph External Services
        TWILIO_API["Twilio Cloud API"]
        PLIVO_API["Plivo Cloud API"]
        DEEPGRAM["Deepgram ASR"]
        OPENAI["OpenAI / LiteLLM"]
        ELEVENLABS["ElevenLabs TTS"]
    end

    PHONE["📞 Phone Call"]

    PHONE --> TWILIO_API
    TWILIO_API -->|"HTTP callback"| TWILIO_APP
    TWILIO_APP -->|"streams via WebSocket"| BOLNA
    BOLNA --> REDIS
    BOLNA --> DEEPGRAM
    BOLNA --> OPENAI
    BOLNA --> ELEVENLABS
    NGROK -->|"public URLs for"| TWILIO_APP
    NGROK -->|"public URLs for"| BOLNA
```

